Introduction
============

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/badge/docs-latest-brightgreen.svg?style=flat
   :target: http://guillotina.readthedocs.io/en/latest/

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/plone/guillotina.svg?branch=master
